{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","role":"symbol","title":"progress","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"property"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The pack’s current progress."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-requestProgress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}]}]}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePack","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Posted by the shared "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object when an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgress":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogress","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A structure containing information about an offline pack’s current download"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"progress."}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/progress":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The pack’s current progress."}],"role":"symbol","title":"progress","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"identifier"}]}}}